{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji21.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致东北局电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致东北局电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年4月18日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我应力争保持长春于我手中，如我能在四平地区大量歼灭顽军，此种可能性是有的。但自前尚难作最后决定，须看斗争结果如何而定。在未作最后决定前，你们应作长期保持计划。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东在得知东北民主联军占领长春消息后致东北局电的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":4,"day":18}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":256,"page_end":256},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}